  "general_provisions": "This bill establishes comprehensive ethics standards, complaint procedures, and enforcement mechanisms for members of the State Board of Education.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>establishes a code of official conduct for State Board of Education members in statute;<hr><ltbullet>creates requirements for conflict of interest disclosures and ethics training;<hr><ltbullet>establishes procedures for filing ethics complaints against board members;<hr><ltbullet>creates an independent ethics commission to investigate complaints;<hr><ltbullet>establishes hearing procedures, evidentiary standards, and due process protections;<hr><ltbullet>provides for disciplinary actions for violations;<hr><ltbullet>establishes confidentiality requirements and contempt provisions; and<hr><ltbullet>provides authority for subpoenas and witness examination.",
